<section class="section section--alt" id="surfing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div>
        <h2>Learn to Surf (Without Pressure)</h2>
        <p>Never surfed before? Or even seen the ocean? No problem!</p>
        <p>
          With 33 years of coaching and teaching rooted in the methods of Surfing Life Club,
          we focus on strong fundamentals that create real, lasting progress.
        </p>
        <p>Many guests return for their second, third or fourth trip to move from beginner to intermediate and beyond!</p>
